OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fextensively cloudy during the evening
OL,7,Fand overnight, with some low-level
OL,8,Fmist and haze. Cloud may be thick
OL,9,Fenough for the odd spot of drizzle in
OL,10,Fplaces, although staying dry for most.
OL,11,FCloud-cover helping to prevent a
OL,12,Ffrost. Light winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FA murky start with extensive
OL,15,Flow cloud, although there is a chance
OL,16,Fof some limited bright or sunny
OL,17,Fintervals developing later. Milder
OL,18,Fthan on Saturday for most. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
