OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,6,Fmurky Monday with patchy rain.
OL,7,FBreezier and perhaps showery Tuesday,
OL,8,Fwith cloud breaks developing. Wet and
OL,9,Fwindy early Wednesday, but soon
OL,10,Fbrighter. Temperatures above average
OL,11,Fday and night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
